      <h1 class="title">Invited Expert and Collaborator Agreement &mdash; 01 June 2015 Edition</h1>
          <ul class="w3c_toc">
            <li class="toc_prefix">On this page → </li>
            <li><a href="#L83">W3C Process</a><span class="bullet"> • </span></li>
            <li><a href="#L160">Participation cost</a><span class="bullet"> • </span></li>
            <li><a href="#L164">Notifications</a><span class="bullet"> • </span></li>
            <li><a href="#L172">Duration and Termination</a><span class="bullet"> • </span></li>
